                                    <a href="/en/about-hempel/news/2017/helping-girls-get-involved-in-science">
                                        Helping girls get involved in science
                                    </a>
                                </h3>
                            </div> 
                            <div class="newsfront__date">
                                <p>
                                    30-08-2017
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="newsfront__news-text">
                                <p>
                                    We need to get more girls interested in science. This is the premise behind Girls Day in Science in Denmark, and one were keen to help out with. For the second year running, local schoolgirls visited our labs in Lyngby ...
                                </p>

                        <div class="newsfront__news">

                                        Hempel Family Day enjoys preview of Sailing World Championships
                                    </a>
                                </h3>
                            </div> 
                            <div class="newsfront__date">
                                <p>
                                    15-08-2017
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="newsfront__news-text">
                                <p>
                                    We held Hempel Family Day at Eg Marina in Aarhus, Denmark last Saturday. 130 people gathered for a picnic and activities by the sea, including watching test races for the Hempel Sailing Word Championships next year.
                                </p>
